\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

We found the forward-chaining diagrammatic proofs intuitive, but they cannot
 prove hard theorems alone
\begin_inset Formula $\ldots$
\end_inset

 [The] backward-chaining diagrammatic proofs [are] less intuitive but they
 can be used to prove hard theorems.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
